01:31.295 --> 01:33.663
- My zucchini casserole.
- Zucchini?

01:33.731 --> 01:36.733
(chuckles) Excuse me, but
this is not Italian squash.

01:36.801 --> 01:39.235
Yeah, the only thing Italian
about this situation

01:39.303 --> 01:40.537
